{"tid":1428721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［尖咀觀星］狗出手想逆轉民意","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:34:36.000Z","uid":113548,"like":71,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7e3e91550bf809ea7faa929518c3e43872e852","tid":1428721,"uid":113548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:46:56.000Z","msg":"第一次開post<br />\n<br />\n今晚尖沙咀碼頭有和平活動<br />\n但旁晚狗已經吹大雞叫人閂門<br />\n擺晒大水馬 仲已經落重兵力查車查人<br />\n製造示威=恐襲既氣氛<br />\n好明顯劇本係今晚會武力清場<br />\n然後又拉幾個 <br />\n再博你又圍狗屋 放火 掟野 etc.<br />\n<br />\n之後遣責 務求塑造黑衫=暴徒<br />\n玩多幾次<br />\n然後民意逆轉革命收皮<br />\n<br />\n8.5之後已經開始有轉風向既跡象<br />\n今晚希望各位 be water 和理非<br />\n小心周邊有25狗<br />\n盡量盡量唔好比位人入<br />\n場仗仲有排打 一輸就輸成世"},{"pid":"e7af02b7db3a224f45ad567b42395b2193d4f4b1","tid":1428721,"uid":38737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"和平觀星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eacf875005bc3cd126f5595f770934bea286781","tid":1428721,"uid":113548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9cc3b7b550de60c2ba155317bf30510f338c8ab5","tid":1428721,"uid":113548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bb5ab96876bed0eb2f8e59c0e029c162aa6dd21","tid":1428721,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:49:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我建議文宣方向<br />\n<br />\n針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n